Thank you for teaching me how to shoot a free throw, hit a golf ball and how to love my ‚Äòsweetie pie‚Äô with all that I have. Those who knew you have a peace knowing that you are hanging out, dancing, and probably telling really loud, funny stories in heaven. Thank you Lord for letting us have Bruce Norman for 84 years... he was truly a blessing. I love you Big Dad... save me a tee time.

Dear Imperial Star Destroyer, to most, you would have just been a standard, everyday, 80+ hour LEGO build. But to me, you were so much more than that. You were my friend. My best friend. Rest in pieces good buddy. #rip
